xbrli:xbrl.in-capmkt:TopicsOrPrinciplesCoveredUnder:
During the Financial Year 2024-25, the Company had
conducted the following trainings for the Board of
Directors on the Principles of NGRBC:
1. Training on prevention of Sexual Harassment of
women at workplace;
2. Diversity Training
3. Human Rights training;
4. Anti-corruption & Anti Bribery training;
5. Training on Conflict of Interest;
6. Business Ethics training; and
7. Training on Structured Digital Database under SEBI
(Prohibition of Insider Trading) Regulations, 2015
